title: Add digit counter, clean up threading model, make scroll text smaller

title: Remove initial display pause
message:
Remove initial display pause

This does not play nice with the new buffered display. It was pausing,
displaying a few digits, and then scrolling very quickly. Now it immediately
starts scrolling quickly.

title: Limit text view update frequency
message:
Limit text view update frequency

Limit adding digits to the text view to 4 times per second. This eliminates
the choppiness during early calculations. Unfortunately, the beginning
digits no longer display due to very fast calculation of early digits.

title: Further optimize performance
message:
Further optimize performance

Inline loops and hot spot operations to improve performance by 150%.
Logic is currently 10x as efficient since starting optimization.

title: Optimize performance
message:
Optimize performance

Inline loops, cache calculations, and loosen restrictions. Slightly more
than doubles overall performance.

title: Implement BBP in C++
message:
Implement BBP in C++

While the project is now in dire need of cleanup, there is a basic working
implementation of the BBP algorithm in C++. The precision fails quickly,
so the project will need an arbitrary precision arithmetic library for
further development.

title: Integrate Google Test using Android.mk and adb
message:
Integrate Google Test using Android.mk and adb

This needs to be integrated into Gradle, but it's not clear how to do that
correctly. Tests would ideally run on Windows, but there's no great way to
support that without introducing an external compiler dependency. Tests
can run on hardware device or simulator.
